channel.title: Compiling error
channel.description:
Okay, well, I was attempting to add a PK zone in a certain area,and I got this error;
src\server\model\players\Player.java:812: error: illegal start of expression public boolean isInHomePK() { ^ src\server\model\players\Player.java:812: error: ';' expected public boolean isInHomePK() { ^ 2 errors Press any key to continue . . .
I'd really appreciate it if someone can help me. I was trying to add this; http://rune - server.com/runescape-development/google/tutorials/372849-pi-yanille-pk-zone-3.html
